      <title>Frederik Valentin &amp; Emil F will present a live concert performing music from the...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DUoSP3yAPea/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/629674327_18059679665672372_3458971237084755276_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzMDM5MTczODYwMjY4MjI2Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEzNTB4MTY4OC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=51rbHo0dWTIQ7kNvwG1-PCC&amp;_nc_oc=Adq0wVSfHMdGA43z4ohGem2aZjshXEHM01iil-sKPUYZyQcuuclHqGUdByRsYIPnnTo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lX6ENCWtvdvjNx673OSU_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwW6LN39DxgZ984hERYLj_i4ZWjdZmIN_v-XNQb3nVeVA&amp;oe=69CA1D08" alt="Instagram billede fra @frederikvalentin" /></p><p><strong>@frederikvalentin</strong></p><p>Frederik Valentin &amp; Emil F will present a live concert performing music from their album Falling Into Fall released on @year0001online <br/>
<br/>
Created over two years across studios in Copenhagen, the project grew from a mentorship into a creative kinship, shaped by curiosity, experimentation, and obsessive attention to detail. The result is a collection of spacious compositions where gentle acoustic gestures drift through natural electronic winds, forming sonic landscapes that feel both weightless and deeply grounded.<br/>
Blending ambient minimalism, folk-inflected melodies, and subtle electronic textures, Falling Into Fall moves through a delicate balance of light and darkness, offering an intimate meditation on transience, impermanence, and the quiet beauty of descent.<br/>
<br/>
Frederik Valentin &amp; Emil F will perform live at 21:00.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/629674327_18059679665672372_3458971237084755276_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzMDM5MTczODYwMjY4MjI2Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEzNTB4MTY4OC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=51rbHo0dWTIQ7kNvwG1-PCC&amp;_nc_oc=Adq0wVSfHMdGA43z4ohGem2aZjshXEHM01iil-sKPUYZyQcuuclHqGUdByRsYIPnnTo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lX6ENCWtvdvjNx673OSU_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwW6LN39DxgZ984hERYLj_i4ZWjdZmIN_v-XNQb3nVeVA&amp;oe=69CA1D08" alt="Instagram billede fra @frederikvalentin" /></p><p><strong>@frederikvalentin</strong></p><p>Frederik Valentin &amp; Emil F will present a live concert performing music from their album Falling Into Fall released on @year0001online <br/>
<br/>
Created over two years across studios in Copenhagen, the project grew from a mentorship into a creative kinship, shaped by curiosity, experimentation, and obsessive attention to detail. The result is a collection of spacious compositions where gentle acoustic gestures drift through natural electronic winds, forming sonic landscapes that feel both weightless and deeply grounded.<br/>
Blending ambient minimalism, folk-inflected melodies, and subtle electronic textures, Falling Into Fall moves through a delicate balance of light and darkness, offering an intimate meditation on transience, impermanence, and the quiet beauty of descent.<br/>
<br/>
Frederik Valentin &amp; Emil F will perform live at 21:00.</p>]]></content:encoded>
