      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/587533913_18546856183020866_1579762302345274091_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4MzEyMTY0MjQyMDI2NDE1OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=AsfAGhXOPdkQ7kNvwFU7Iha&amp;_nc_oc=AdqHQmLkjLsB3Q4RNCfDjQlRrgfdtZJY7PBamh4C43hAE_EG2xROGaQzVZ7r7WdSXLE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lX6ENCWtvdvjNx673OSU_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyCAhBmTtArk1IP4jC9lW28hZM6rPt_isuEsXYOPe3bHw&amp;oe=69CA31BA" alt="Slide 1 fra @frederikvalentin" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/597922666_18546856192020866_2191114053647292833_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4MzEyMTY0MjQyODYzNzgxNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=PohZk0AlickQ7kNvwGwASnB&amp;_nc_oc=AdoCKa0rx_4n4tdz64aWOEqCuevZY_7x_ZvG04Dt7zmnW7wpBs4w82X3iHe3dSL4FVw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lX6ENCWtvdvjNx673OSU_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy20UtS_ieRJ4Ge8AnSwhmbo6bEvGue57xVTWIU4yOSfw&amp;oe=69CA2672" alt="Slide 2 fra @frederikvalentin" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (2 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@frederikvalentin</strong></p><p>On Friday, I released a new full-length album Falling Into Fall, created in collaboration with Emil F (@emiliomburg).<br/>
<br/>
Emil and I first met when he was a student at the Rhythmic Music Conservatory in Copenhagen, where I was brought in to mentor his bachelor project. Not long after, we began exploring music together—writing our own songs and producing for other artists—and this album grew naturally out of that creative partnership.<br/>
<br/>
Recorded over three years, Falling Into Fall has been distilling slowly for a long time as we gradually peeled away layers to reveal its true essence.<br/>
<br/>
We are both excited to share it!<br/>
<br/>
“a fall toward something unknown—the beauty of letting go.”<br/>
<br/>
Falling Into Fall is out now on YEAR0001.<br/>
<br/>
Artwork by Noa Lachmi @noalachmi<br/>
Layout by Victor Svedberg @axisvictor<br/>
Photography by Betty Krag @BettyKrag</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DSAWRhpjVT8/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/587533913_18546856183020866_1579762302345274091_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4MzEyMTY0MjQyMDI2NDE1OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=AsfAGhXOPdkQ7kNvwFU7Iha&amp;_nc_oc=AdqHQmLkjLsB3Q4RNCfDjQlRrgfdtZJY7PBamh4C43hAE_EG2xROGaQzVZ7r7WdSXLE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lX6ENCWtvdvjNx673OSU_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyCAhBmTtArk1IP4jC9lW28hZM6rPt_isuEsXYOPe3bHw&amp;oe=69CA31BA" alt="Slide 1 fra @frederikvalentin" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/597922666_18546856192020866_2191114053647292833_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4MzEyMTY0MjQyODYzNzgxNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=PohZk0AlickQ7kNvwGwASnB&amp;_nc_oc=AdoCKa0rx_4n4tdz64aWOEqCuevZY_7x_ZvG04Dt7zmnW7wpBs4w82X3iHe3dSL4FVw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lX6ENCWtvdvjNx673OSU_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy20UtS_ieRJ4Ge8AnSwhmbo6bEvGue57xVTWIU4yOSfw&amp;oe=69CA2672" alt="Slide 2 fra @frederikvalentin" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (2 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@frederikvalentin</strong></p><p>On Friday, I released a new full-length album Falling Into Fall, created in collaboration with Emil F (@emiliomburg).<br/>
<br/>
Emil and I first met when he was a student at the Rhythmic Music Conservatory in Copenhagen, where I was brought in to mentor his bachelor project. Not long after, we began exploring music together—writing our own songs and producing for other artists—and this album grew naturally out of that creative partnership.<br/>
<br/>
Recorded over three years, Falling Into Fall has been distilling slowly for a long time as we gradually peeled away layers to reveal its true essence.<br/>
<br/>
We are both excited to share it!<br/>
<br/>
“a fall toward something unknown—the beauty of letting go.”<br/>
<br/>
Falling Into Fall is out now on YEAR0001.<br/>
<br/>
Artwork by Noa Lachmi @noalachmi<br/>
Layout by Victor Svedberg @axisvictor<br/>
Photography by Betty Krag @BettyKrag</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DSAWRhpjVT8/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
